    "body": "Closes #4438.\r\n\r\nSince v0.22.0 gopls no longer advertises semantic tokens for clients by default.\r\nTo maintain previous behavior, semantic tokens are enabled on client side.\r\n\r\nThis change will take effect after gopls v0.22.1 release.\r\n",
